
AOM-style civ-selection dialog for 0AD : Empires Ascendant


Description
------------------------------------------------------------------------
"Age of Mythology" style Civilisation Selection Dialog for use with the
Match Setup page. Based on a mockup by Mythos_Ruler.

Installation
------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Acquire zip
   - (https://github.com/s0600204/0ad-civselection-mod/archive/master.zip)
2. Move to your mods folder, default locations are:
   - Linux   : ~/.local/share/0ad/mods
   - OSX     : ~/Library/Application\ Support/0ad/mods
   - Windows : "Documents" or "My Documents" Folder => My Games\0ad\mods\
3. Unzip archive
4. Rename the resulting folder to "civselect"
5. Start 0AD
6. From main menu, "Tools & Options" > "Mod Selection"
7. Select "civselect" from upper section
8. Press buttons captioned with "Enable", "Save Configuration", and then
   "Start Mods" in that order
9. Go to start a new match/game.

